Distribution. Central Europe (Alps), North Europe (Scandinavia, Finland , N. Russia ) ( Kopelke 1991 ), Siberia ( Zhelochovtsev & Zinovjev 1995 ), and arctic Canada (
Hjältén et al. 2003
).

Occurrence in Sweden: published records; Uppland, Jämtland, Norrbotten (Haris 2009), Lule Lappmark, Torne Lappmark (
Vikberg 1970
).
